<h2 class="box__heading">Professional Learning and Leadership Directorate</h2>
<p>Our team has the strategic responsibility for ensuring high quality professional learning for education professionals across Scotland.</p>
</a>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
