<h2 class="box__heading">What we offer</h2>
<p>We support education professionals to make a difference in the classroom, school and wider community through access to innovative and quality professional learning and leadership development programmes and activities.</p>
</a>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
